modules.description: This module implements the Salsa20 stream cipher, providing encryption and decryption operations using 32-byte or 16-byte keys and 8-byte nonces. It supports the full Salsa20/20 core function as well as reduced variants Salsa20/8 and Salsa20/12 for generating the internal state. Typical use cases include secure data transmission and cryptographic protocols requiring high-speed, nonce-based encryption.
